wala.

268
00:16:16,310 --> 00:16:17,325
ano yun?

269
00:16:17,350 --> 00:16:18,646
[tumawa]

270
00:16:18,935 --> 00:16:20,979
Saka bakit ang haba ng mukha?

271
00:16:21,138 --> 00:16:22,169
[Tumawa si Yuri]

272
00:16:22,814 --> 00:16:23,982
Hindi nakakatuwa yun.

273
00:16:26,359 --> 00:16:27,819
Ano bang problema mo Jay?

274
00:16:28,612 --> 00:16:29,696
Maaari mo itong ibahagi sa akin.

275
00:16:31,948 --> 00:16:33,116
Tungkol ito kay Aries.

276
00:16:34,326 --> 00:16:35,568
Anong nangyari sa kanya?

277
00:16:36,202 --> 00:16:39,914
Parang may nasabi akong masama sa kanya.
Bigla na lang siyang umiyak.

278
00:16:40,985 --> 00:16:42,029
Seryoso?

279
00:16:42,471 --> 00:16:43,701
Umiyak si Aries?

280
00:16:44,127 --> 00:16:45,127
Oo.

281
00:16:45,337 --> 00:16:49,007
Nag-uusap lang kami tungkol sa kapatid ni Felix.

282
00:16:49,924 --> 00:16:51,134
Ano nga ulit pangalan niya?

283
00:16:52,761 --> 00:16:53,783
Bawat...

284
00:16:53,808 --> 00:16:55,851
Percy? Percy! yun lang.

285
00:16:58,381 --> 00:16:59,733
Bakit mo siya pinag-uusapan?

286
00:17:00,185 --> 00:17:02,687
Hindi naman talaga namin siya pinag-uusapan.
tanong ko lang.

287
00:17:03,141 --> 00:17:04,763
Nag-usap kami ni Felix.

288
00:17:05,023 --> 00:17:06,865
Sinabi niya sa akin ang tungkol sa kanyang kapatid.

289
00:17:07,275 --> 00:17:09,736
So, tinanong ko si Aries. At ayun, nag-away kami.

290
