Sumali sa laro.

293
00:17:22,999 --> 00:17:25,644
- Halika!
- Mabilis, samahan mo kami!

294
00:17:25,669 --> 00:17:26,728
Tara na.

295
00:17:26,753 --> 00:17:28,037
Maglaro tayo sa kanila.

296
00:17:30,840 --> 00:17:32,380
Halika na! Laro tayo.

297
00:17:33,059 --> 00:17:35,195
Kung hindi ka makasagot,
magbabayad ka ng limang daan.

298
00:17:35,220 --> 00:17:37,180
- Jay, mauna ka na.
- Hindi, gagawin niya ito.

299
00:17:37,555 --> 00:17:42,369
[nagdaldal]

300
00:17:42,394 --> 00:17:44,479
- Subukan lang ang isa. Isa lang.
- Hulaan natin ito.

301
00:17:45,063 --> 00:17:46,564
Okay. Go, go, go.

302
00:17:46,982 --> 00:17:48,130
- Sige na! Gawin mo lang!
- Mabilis!

303
00:17:48,544 --> 00:17:49,567
[tumawa]

304
00:17:49,576 --> 00:17:50,951
[tumawa]

305
00:17:51,474 --> 00:17:52,482
Gawin mo, bilis!

306
00:17:52,946 --> 00:17:55,090
- Teka, iniisip ko!
- Oh, so may utak ka?

307
00:17:55,115 --> 00:17:56,174
Lima,

308
00:17:56,199 --> 00:17:57,742
- apat,
- tatlo,

309
00:17:57,767 --> 00:17:59,285
- dalawa,
- isa!

310
00:17:59,285 --> 00:18:01,349
- Hindi ko ginagawa iyon.
- [ang mga lalaki ay umuungol sa pagkabigo]

311
00:18:04,749 --> 00:18:07,224
Salamat po ma'am. The best ang tapa mo!

312
00:18:11,185 --> 00:18:13,508
Kaya, sir, kailan natin makukuha ang kotse?

313
00:18:13,533 --> 00:18:15,748
- Kinabukasan.
- Sa susunod na araw?

314
00:18:17,810 --> 00:18:18,935
- Masyadong mahaba yan!
- Psst! Hoy!

315
00:18:19,959 --> 00:18:21,263
Hoy, Jay!

316
00:18:21,975 --> 00:18:23,808
- Kumusta ka na?
- Ano ang balak niyo?

317
00:18:25,061 --> 00:18:26,454
Nasira ang sasakyan ko.

318
00:18:26,479 --> 00:18:27,580
Kaya, kinailangan kong ayusin ito.

319
00:18:27,605 --> 00:18:30,787
Gusto kong sumakay pero ako
natapos din sa paglalakad.

320
00:18:31,482 --> 00:18:32,502
Ay, Jay!

321
00:18:32,527 --> 00:18:34,115
Malapit na ang school festival, di ba?

322
00:18:34,140 --> 00:18:35,296
tama yan!

323
00:18:35,321 --> 00:18:37,924
Wala pa rin kami
mga kinatawan para sa paligsahan.

324
00:18:37,949 --> 00:18:38,949
ginagawa namin.

325
00:18:39,325 --> 00:18:40,325
- WHO?
- WHO?

326
00:18:40,744 --> 00:18:42,178
Tingnan mong mabuti ang isa't isa.

327
00:18:42,203 --> 00:18:43,955
Si Mr Pretty at Ms. Gwapo.

328
00:18:45,165 --> 00:18:47,392
Well, obvious naman na gagawin ko
mapili para kay Ms.Gwapo.

329
00:18:47,417 --> 00:18:48,893
Ako lang ang babae kaya no choice.

330
00:18:48,918 --> 00:18:50,599
Pero Ci-N para kay Mr. Pretty?

331
00:18:50,962 --> 00:18:52,279
- Hindi ako sigurado.
- Oo, bakit ako?

332
00:18:52,672 --> 00:18:53,898
Binuo ka na parang babae.

333
00:18:53,923 --> 00:18:55,775
- Baliw ka. Susuntukin kita.
- Sige, subukan mo lang.

334
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:56,401
Subukan ito!

335
00:18:56,426 --> 00:18:58,091
- Sige, hahalikan kita. Walang malisya.
- Kaya, ano?

336
00:18:58,116 --> 00:18:59,279
[Tumili si Jay-jay]

337
00:18:59,304 --> 00:19:00,537
- [Ci-N chuckles]
- Ci-N, ang tanga mo!

338
00:19:00,685 --> 00:19:02,216
Masyado pang maaga, pero
napakagulo mo na.

339
00:19:02,241 --> 00:19:03,552
Bakit mo ginawa yun bro?

340
00:19:04,341 --> 00:19:05,827
- Halik, halik, halik. Laro.
- Bro, kakaiba ka.

341
00:19:05,852 --> 00:19:07,287
Tigilan mo yang kakaibang kalokohan na yan bro.

342
00:19:07,312 --> 00:19:08,438
Please, itigil mo na yang weird shit na yan.

343
00:19:08,438 --> 00:19:09,459
Tumigil ka! Tumigil ka!

344
00:19:10,857 --> 00:19:11,990
Nakakainis ka pare.

345
00:19:12,817 --> 00:19:14,044
[Sumisigaw si Jay-jay]

346
00:19:14,069 --> 00:19:15,862
- Hoy, kuya! Jay-jay!
- Umalis ka sa akin! Tulungan mo ako!

347
00:19:16,070 --> 00:19:17,740
- Hoy! Hoy!
- Jay-jay!

348
00:19:18,659 --> 00:19:20,661
Hoy! Tumigil ka! Anong ginagawa mo?!

349
00:19:23,154 --> 00:19:24,262
Jay!

350
00:19:24,287 --> 00:19:26,529
- [beatboxing]
- Tingnan mo ako.

351
00:19:26,554 --> 00:19:27,748
Halika, halika. Ikaw muna.

352
00:19:28,025 --> 00:19:29,559
Sa langit, may anghel.

353
00:19:29,584 --> 00:19:30,794
Sa dagat, may kabibi.

354
00:19:30,794 --> 00:19:32,128
Nakita ko ang kalbo mong tatay,

355
00:19:32,128 --> 00:19:33,505
- paglalagay ng ilang hair gel.
- Ano ang bumabagabag sa iyo?

356
00:19:33,530 --> 00:19:34,906
[Nagpapa-hype ang mga lalaki]

357
00:19:36,951 --> 00:19:39,638
Sinabi ni [Yuri] Aries kay Jay-jay ang tungkol kay Percy.

358
00:19:40,896 --> 00:19:41,896
Keifer!

359
00:19:42,185 --> 00:19:43,257
Keifer!

360
00:19:43,282 --> 00:19:44,849
Ano ba yang sinisigawan mo?

361
00:19:44,945 --> 00:19:46,797
- Ito ay Jay-jay!
- Anong nangyari kay Jay-jay?!

362
00:19:46,822 --> 00:19:47,827
Kinuha nila siya!

363
00:19:47,852 --> 00:19:49,787
- Mga tao ni Ram. sigurado ako.
- Ano?!

364
00:19:50,492 --> 00:19:52,310
Walang lumalabas sa kwartong ito.

365
00:19:52,357 --> 00:19:53,374
Ito ay isang bitag.

366
00:19:53,399 --> 00:19:55,543
Wala tayong magagawa dito, Keifer!

367
00:19:55,568 --> 00:19:57,320
Alam ko kung paano maglaro si Ram.

368
00:19:57,445 --> 00:19:58,922
Aakayin niya tayo sa kanyang laro,

369
00:19:58,947 --> 00:20:00,799
at pagkatapos ay magiging tayo ang
sa huli ay matatalo.

370
00:20:00,824 --> 00:20:03,009
- Kung gayon ano ang iyong plano?!
- Hindi tayo pwedeng manatili lang dito, Keifer!

371
00:20:03,034 --> 00:20:04,396
alam ko! iniisip ko!

372
00:20:04,959 --> 00:20:07,404
[tunog ng telepono]

373
00:20:07,781 --> 00:20:09,174
- Ano yun?
- Sino ang tumatawag?

374
00:20:09,199 --> 00:20:10,216
Si Ram naman! Si Ram naman!

375
00:20:11,370 --> 00:20:12,802
- Sino yun?
- Isara mo ang iyong bibig!

376
00:20:13,336 --> 00:20:14,521
- Jay!
- Jay!

377
00:20:14,546 --> 00:20:16,047
- Jay!
- Jay!

378
00:20:16,072 --> 00:20:20,099
[Ram] Hey, hey, hey. Huwag masyadong maingay.
Hindi mo ba nakikita, may natutulog?

379
00:20:21,634 --> 00:20:24,011
Hi, boys! Anong meron?

380
00:20:24,639 --> 00:20:26,721
- Na-miss ako?
- Oo. marami.

381
00:20:27,183 --> 00:20:28,183
Fuck you!

382
00:20:28,518 --> 00:20:29,811
Alam mo...

383
00:20:30,032 --> 00:20:31,396
medyo naputol yung last game namin.

384
00:20:31,980 --> 00:20:33,106
Ipagpatuloy natin ito.

385
00:20:33,731 --> 00:20:35,943
- Tayo ba?
- Anong gagawin mo kay Jay-jay?!

386
00:20:36,484 --> 00:20:37,569
Sa totoo lang,

387
00:20:38,069 --> 00:20:39,294
hindi ko talaga alam.

388
00:20:40,196 --> 00:20:42,198
Pero naiinis ako sa ginawa niya.

389
00:20:42,647 --> 00:20:44,615
sus. Naramdaman kong niloko ako.

390
00:20:45,227 --> 00:20:46,328
Speaking of.

391
00:20:46,376 --> 00:20:48,295
Masyado kang maingay. Gising na siya ngayon.

392
00:20:48,746 --> 00:20:50,529
- Jay!
- Jay-jay!

393
00:20:51,374 --> 00:20:53,001
Gumising ka, sleepyhead.

394
00:20:53,751 --> 00:20:55,263
Ram, anong gusto mo?!

395
00:20:55,587 --> 00:20:56,796
Bisitahin ang iyong kaibigan.

396
00:20:57,463 --> 00:20:59,623
Ngunit limitado lamang ang aking tinatanggap na mga bisita.

397
00:21:00,466 --> 00:21:01,509
Baka...

398
00:21:02,218 --> 00:21:03,344
apat na tao lang.

399
00:21:03,373 --> 00:21:04,487
Apat lang?!

400
00:21:04,512 --> 00:21:05,818
[Nagtatalo ang mga lalaki sa Section E]

401
00:21:07,654 --> 00:21:09,225
- Manahimik ka!
- Fuck mo, asong babae!

402
00:21:09,250 --> 00:21:11,119
Sige! Magiging apat na lang tayo.
ilan ka na?

403
00:21:11,144 --> 00:21:13,813
Hoy, ngayon... Kung ako sayo, gagawin ko
pag-aagawan mo ako dito.

404
00:21:14,544 --> 00:21:15,552
Tingnan mo...

405
00:21:16,649 --> 00:21:17,942
Hindi ako mahilig magsawa.

406
00:21:18,294 --> 00:21:19,294
Itigil mo na!

407
00:21:19,319 --> 00:21:21,419
- Jay!
- Ang gago mo! Anak ng asungot!

408
00:21:22,322 --> 00:21:24,443
Alam mo kung saan ako hahanapin.

409
00:21:27,785 --> 00:21:28,887
Yuri!

410
00:21:28,912 --> 00:21:30,388
Nagsasayang ka ng lakas.

411
00:21:30,413 --> 00:21:31,431
Tara na!

412
00:21:31,456 --> 00:21:33,725
David! Ci-N! Kumuha ng isa pang kotse.

413
00:21:33,750 --> 00:21:35,501
- Pupunta kaming apat.
- Seryoso ka?!

414
00:21:35,526 --> 00:21:37,228
Hindi namin maaaring ipagsapalaran ang anumang bagay.

415
00:21:37,253 --> 00:21:38,938
Apat lang ang sinabi ni Ram.

416
00:21:38,963 --> 00:21:41,733
Ngunit tulad ng dati,
nagdadala kami ng back-up na sasakyan.

417
00:21:41,758 --> 00:21:43,718
Eren, siguraduhin mong walang makakakita sa iyo.

418
00:21:43,968 --> 00:21:45,107
Tara na!

419
00:21:45,788 --> 00:21:47,316
- Ilipat, mabilis.
- Halika!

420
00:21:48,715 --> 00:21:50,534
- Ano ang plano?
- Halika. Tara na!

421
00:21:50,558 --> 00:21:52,352
Hello! Saan ang impiyerno
ikaw ba! Halika na dali!

422
00:21:52,352 --> 00:21:53,745
- [Ci-N] Nasaan ka?
- Malapit na tayo sa parking.

423
00:21:53,770 --> 00:21:56,714
- Pupunta kami sa kotse ni David.
- Sige. Bilisan mo lang.

424
00:21:57,857 --> 00:21:59,308
Nasaan si Jay-jay?!

425
00:21:59,567 --> 00:22:00,972
Tinawag ni Ram si Kiko!

426
00:22:01,235 --> 00:22:03,321
Sigurado akong naligaw siya
sa gulo mo na naman!

427
00:22:03,377 --> 00:22:04,663
Isipin ang iyong sariling negosyo!

428
00:22:04,697 --> 00:22:05,711
Ililigtas natin si Jay-jay!

429
00:22:05,736 --> 00:22:07,308
Ililigtas ko ang pinsan ko.

430
00:22:07,762 --> 00:22:09,043
- Sasamahan ka namin.
- Hindi mo kaya.

431
00:22:09,577 --> 00:22:11,095
Apat na tao lang ang hinihingi ni Ram.

432
00:22:11,120 --> 00:22:13,748
Dito ka na lang. Naglalagay ka
Jay-jay at risk sa ginagawa mo.

433
00:22:13,923 --> 00:22:15,183
- Tayo na!
- Teka.

434
00:22:17,252 --> 00:22:20,004
- I-report na lang natin.
- Hindi. Kilala ko si Ram.

435
00:22:20,088 --> 00:22:21,881
Papasok pa si Jay-jay
panganib kung gagawin natin iyon.

436
00:22:22,238 --> 00:22:23,293
At saka ano?

437
00:22:23,800 --> 00:22:25,425
Hindi mo ba sasabihin sa kapatid mo?

438
00:22:33,184 --> 00:22:34,602
Nasaan na kayo guys? Ano kaya ang tagal?

439
00:22:34,627 --> 00:22:37,160
[Ci-N] Maghintay ka! Malapit na tayo.
Naipit lang sa stoplight.

440
00:22:37,188 --> 00:22:38,481
- Bilisan mo lang dito.
- [Ci-N] Okay, okay.

441
00:22:41,109 --> 00:22:43,699
Babatukan ko sila
kung hinawakan nila siya. I swear.

442
00:22:47,198 --> 00:22:48,910
Keifer, may itatanong ako sayo.

443
00:22:49,158 --> 00:22:50,410
Kailangan mo bang itanong ito ngayon?

444
00:22:52,996 --> 00:22:55,668
May nangyari ba sa inyo
at Jay-jay sa Horror House?

445
00:23:00,586 --> 00:23:02,338
Teka, tanungin muna kita.

446
00:23:04,173 --> 00:23:05,675
Gusto mo ba si Jay-jay?

447
00:23:06,175 --> 00:23:07,343
May nararamdaman ka ba sa kanya?

448
00:23:17,979 --> 00:23:18,979
Oo.

449
00:23:21,315 --> 00:23:22,900
Nahuhulog na yata ako sa kanya.

450
00:23:25,236 --> 00:23:26,511
Nasisiraan ka na ba ng bait?

451
00:23:27,155 --> 00:23:28,293
Alam mo may plano tayo.

452
00:23:28,573 --> 00:23:30,116
Parte pa rin ba ito ng plano mo?

453
00:23:31,159 --> 00:23:32,844
Lahat ng nangyari
sa amusement park.

454
00:23:32,869 --> 00:23:34,262
Ang pangyayari kay Aries.

455
00:23:34,287 --> 00:23:36,039
At ngayon, iniligtas namin siya mula kay Ram.

456
00:23:36,456 --> 00:23:37,473
Syempre.

457
00:23:37,498 --> 00:23:38,691
Nagsisimula ka na bang magduda sa akin?

458
00:23:39,584 --> 00:23:40,960
Nakita mo kung gaano nag-aalala si Aries.

459
00:23:41,419 --> 00:23:43,588
May pakialam siya kay Jay-jay.
Parte pa rin ito ng plano.

460
00:23:44,894 --> 00:23:45,902
totoo ba yun?

461
00:23:48,801 --> 00:23:51,300
Dahil nakikita ko iyong concern mo
para siyang nagiging totoo.

462
00:23:52,138 --> 00:23:53,675
Bakit mo ginagawa ito, Keifer?

463
00:24:00,063 --> 00:24:01,981
Alam mong kailangan ko siya para sa plano ko, Yuri.

464
00:24:11,282 --> 00:24:13,951
- Nasaan sila?!
- Tayo na! Napakabagal mo!

